name: Camper Van T-Shirt For Babies
description:
Retro style VW Camper Van t-shirt for babies. 

Love VW Camper Vans?  Love babies?  Now you can combine the two loves of your life with this cute little sketch design of a retro VW Camper Van on a super soft, 100 % cotton t-shirt for babies.

Each t-shirt is lovingly printed by hand to order with eco-friendly water based inks.  If you would prefer a colour not listed then just let us know to see if we have it!

name: Toy Robot T-Shirt For Babies
description:
The Robots are Coming! Let this cute toy robot come marching right on in ... The perfect gift for the robot-mad babies in your life. 

This toy robot looks space age but unfortunately we cannot guarantee that he will be able to help round the house! 

Hand printed on to a 100% cotton t-shirt, we have offered some colour options below but if you would prefer a colour not listed then just e-mail us to see if we have it!

name: Robots VS Dinos
description:
In the eternal battle of Robots Versus Dinosaurs, which side are you on?  In the purple circle we have the gangly robot and in the green circle we have the slightly bewildered looking dinosaur.  Okay then, they might not look like the most terrifying contestants, or even like they are locked in fierce battle... but they do look mighty cute together on this ever-practical grey t-shirt (grey shows up the dirt less!).
Hand printed with love and care, and three inks, on to a super soft 100% cotton t-shirt by us in Bristol.  Each t-shirt is printed to order and is custom finished by us too.
